  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオス城の中……変わってないな、
あの時のまんまだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I couldn't see things through to the end back then... Things look the same as then.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふしぎ空間だからね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's a pretty interesting time-space, here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私の心もあの時のまんま</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My heart is just as shaken as back then, too...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>構やしない。初心忘るべからずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't fill yourself up with concern. Remember your original resolution.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Klarth&gt;、おっさんくさいってば</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Always with the old man talk...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>初心とか、そんなんじゃないんだ。
ダオスと顔合わせるのが怖いだけ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I didn't really have so much resolution as much as I was utterly scared to meet with Dhaos again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、ダオス城の場所知ってたのに
近づかなかったんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So then why did you enter Dhaos's Castle if you're shaken up?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>双子ちゃんに背中を押してもらっちゃった。
情けないなあ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The twins kinda shoved me inside forcibly. No use cryin' now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>恋する乙女はみんな
そんなもんよ♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is the way of a young lady in love~!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46888</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちゃかすなよな、おまえは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're one to poke fun at other people...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いいのいいの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine, it's fine~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47056</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、&lt;Arche&gt;先輩は、
いつも積極的じゃないですかぁ∀</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't &lt;Arche&gt; such an assertive young lady~?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47132</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いやーん、そうかなあ♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hohohoho, yes I am!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47244</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……『おっさん』には、
つきあってられないな、&lt;Chester&gt;行くぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Grandpa will leave you two alone. Let's go &lt;Chester&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_103_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おい待て、オレはおっさんじゃねーぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey wait! I'm no old man!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
